    "description": "If you're reading this, then you probably just died and got thrown out of Heaven. Sorry about that. Good news, though; you get to be on a gameshow!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/8b53cca61593fba68a3f43101e016eaf.poster.avif?t=1693800701\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/8b53cca61593fba68a3f43101e016eaf.webm?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/8b53cca61593fba68a3f43101e016eaf.mp4?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Conquer Hell With Love and Snuggles!</strong><br>Fall For You is a rhythm-based roguelike. Dash and attack with the beat, win the hearts of every damned soul you meet, traverse perilous obstacle courses, win fabulous prizes that change the way you play, and cuddle with a scary demon mom to keep yourself going!<br><br><strong>Dance Party!</strong><br>Dash when the kick drum kicks, and attack when the snare drum snares!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/873dfc1a1cf138c9a6794a510daa16f9.poster.avif?t=1693800701\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/873dfc1a1cf138c9a6794a510daa16f9.webm?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/873dfc1a1cf138c9a6794a510daa16f9.mp4?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Friends in Unexpected Places!</strong><br>Shoot fellow damned souls with Cuddle Bullets to earn their admiration! Do battle with the Underworld's scariest foes!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/9b0bbd5f2560701d712ef015bc9fd431.poster.avif?t=1693800701\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/9b0bbd5f2560701d712ef015bc9fd431.webm?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/9b0bbd5f2560701d712ef015bc9fd431.mp4?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>The World Changes Around You!</strong><br>Stay above the UnderFog, as the world rises and falls around you! Take on procedurally generated challenges to stay in the game and win prizes!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/12f0326e91e5cb553b18e48b455a7d37.poster.avif?t=1693800701\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/12f0326e91e5cb553b18e48b455a7d37.webm?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/12f0326e91e5cb553b18e48b455a7d37.mp4?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fabulous Prizes!</strong><br>Win prizes that change your look, and the way you play!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/c362f4d6abcacb1efa21458cf15a25ce.poster.avif?t=1693800701\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/c362f4d6abcacb1efa21458cf15a25ce.webm?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/c362f4d6abcacb1efa21458cf15a25ce.mp4?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A Place to Rest Your Head</strong><br>Cuddle with a scary demon mom to keep your health bar up! Survive the crazed whims of a self-proclaimed Goddesz of Chaos! Be nice to the twins!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/fc9470b1faa9e643db5261b637678e78.poster.avif?t=1693800701\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/fc9470b1faa9e643db5261b637678e78.webm?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1799730/extras/fc9470b1faa9e643db5261b637678e78.mp4?t=1693800701\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
